{"tid":849772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"強國女10.1澳洲唱《歌唱祖國》   被寸咁偉大就咪出國","createTime":"2018-10-06T03:04:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-06T03:08:28.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d27520536af6a72eefae26458f4e6bdd44d175c3","tid":849772,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T03:04:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181005/large/1538750874_4483.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181005%2Flarge%2F1538750874_4483.jpg&h=ca33f60b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在街頭高唱愛國歌並非大媽專利，日前一名中國女生於十月一日國慶日，在澳洲墨爾本busking（街頭賣唱），這名中國女生架生齊全，拿好咪開大喇叭高唱《歌唱祖國》，並上載片段到社交平台，旋即在抖音及微博被瘋傳。內地網民指她「很親切」、「特別好聽」，亦有網民質疑她炒作，且引吭高歌十分擾民，又寸她既然祖國這麼偉大，就不要跑到外國去。<br />\n<br />\n網上自稱「沙粒小姐-Shelley」的中國女生，於當地畢業後留在墨爾本工作，從其微博可見她不時帶齊相機腳架、音響、咪及擴音喇叭等架生busking。而被瘋傳的短片，是她在本月1日唱《歌唱祖國》，片尾聽到有零星掌聲。她於微博寫道:「想把我的驕傲，我的自豪，我的感恩，在祖國生日這一天唱給所有人聽」。<br />\n<br />\n雖然有不少網民大讚她，稱她「讓我們自豪感爆棚」、「太帥」，但聲量始終太大，有網民稱會對附近居民造成滋擾；被質疑她炒作更無可避免，指既然祖國這麼偉大又怎麼跑去外國。<br />\n<br />\n《歌唱祖國》是一首愛國歌曲。1951年9月12日，已故總理周恩來親自簽發中央人民政府令，要在全國廣泛傳唱此歌。歌曲已成為中國各重大活動的禮儀曲、開場曲或结束曲。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181006/58761351\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181006%2F58761351&d=QiaWgH%2FHQ409H7xcLwSKa0%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=51013d61\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181006%2F58761351&h=b53de5a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181006/58761351</a>"},{"pid":"68fb3de219a85f3f47e36b9e185b57401f9a53ae","tid":849772,"uid":79563,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T03:04:53.000Z","msg":"報比澳洲安全部知啦"},{"pid":"99ccc85cf0f928fe65d37e1aa0de2fa8f9199c34","tid":849772,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T03:06:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1af5a62de045a73895f1850f01c6f3098dea2a3","tid":849772,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T03:07:58.000Z","msg":"On9"},{"pid":"1cc7b21e5fd598e5c2739b29a8776f767a2cfd2f","tid":849772,"uid":50457,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T03:08:28.000Z","msg":"攞住綠卡反美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n攞住香港身份證反港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n攞住中國人身份<br />\n<br />\n。。。<br />\n。。<br />\n。。<br />\n。。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n反自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最反骨的就係蟲國人"}]}